title: OVERNIGHT VEGETABLE & EGG BREAKFAST RECIPE
directions: In a greased 6-qt. slow cooker, layer the first five ingredients. In a large bowl, whisk the next five ingredients; pour over top. Sprinkle with cheese. Cook, covered, on low until potatoes are tender and eggs are set, 7-9 hours. Yield: 8 servings.
ingredients: 4 pounds potatoes, peeled and thinly sliced (about 8 cups)
1 package (10 ounces) frozen chopped spinach, thawed and squeezed dry
